OL,3,CReeves announces pension boost for ex-
OL,4,Cmineworkers
OL,6,FThousands of ex-mineworkers are set to
OL,7,Freceive extra retirement payments
OL,8,Fafter the Chancellor announced she
OL,9,Fwould release funds from a pension
OL,10,Fscheme.
OL,12,FMPs and former pit staff in coalfield
OL,13,Fcommunities have been calling for the
OL,14,Frelease of #2.3 billion in reserves
OL,15,Ffrom the British Coal Staff
OL,16,FSuperannuation Scheme (BCSSS).
