OL,3,CReeves announces pension boost for ex-
OL,4,Cmineworkers
OL,6,FDuring her Budget speech on Wednesday
OL,7,FRachel Reeves said she had made the
OL,8,Fdecision to meet their demands after
OL,9,Fpressure from Labour MPs in Bassetlaw,
OL,10,FMansfield, Barnsley South, Blyth and
OL,11,FAshington and Merthyr.
OL,13,FShe said: "I will transfer the
OL,14,Finvestment reserve fund of the BCSSS
OL,15,Fto its members so that the men and
OL,16,Fwomen who worked in our coal industry
OL,17,Fget a fair deal in their retirement
OL,18,Ftoo."
