OL,3,CReeves announces pension boost for ex-
OL,4,Cmineworkers
OL,6,FNormanton and Hemsworth MP Jon
OL,7,FTrickett said it would help 950
OL,8,Ffamilies in his constituency.
OL,10,FWriting on X he said: "Today they
OL,11,Freceived the justice they deserve
OL,12,F(it's their money!!)."
OL,14,FLabour MP for Easington Grahame Morris
OL,15,Fcalled it "a hard-won victory for all
OL,16,Fin the coal industry".
OL,18,FThe BCSSS began in 1947 but, following
OL,19,Fthe privatisation of the coal industry
OL,20,Fin 1994, the government became a
OL,21,Fguarantor.
