OL,6,FUnder that deal, the government was
OL,7,Fentitled to half the surplus money but
OL,8,Fnothing has been taken since 2015 when
OL,9,Fthat agreement ended.
OL,11,FThe government still guarantees the
OL,12,Fscheme's pension benefits.
OL,14,FAccording to a parliamentary briefing,
OL,15,Fbetween 1995 and 2015 the government
OL,16,Freceived #3.1 billion from the scheme
OL,17,Fand is due to have another payment of
OL,18,F#1.87 billion in 2023.
