OL,3,CReeves announces pension boost for ex-
OL,4,Cmineworkers
OL,6,FThe scheme has about 40,000 members,
OL,7,Fincluding up to 5,000 women and widows
OL,8,Fof former miners.
OL,10,FSix members of the scheme visited
OL,11,FWestminster earlier this month to call
OL,12,Ffor action.
OL,14,FAt the time ex-miner Peter Short told
OL,15,FITV Calendar: "We kept the lights on
OL,16,Fin this country for many years, which
OL,17,Fwas dirty dangerous work.
